        ],
        "headline": "Her family lived in their Morningside Heights home for three generations. After the death of her grandparents, she’s fighting to keep it that way.",
        "dek": "As Columbia’s presence has grown, housing advocates say neighboring residents often struggle for their tenant succession rights following the death of their relatives, leaving little time to grieve.",
